          {
            "title": "Example: Function",
            "id": 74217,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Напиши код с использованием ключевого слова <code>function</code>, чтобы завершить функцию.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"weatherUpdate\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Weather update&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Sunny skies ahead&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"weatherUpdate();\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"8\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Weather update\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Sunny skies ahead\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>function</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Function name",
            "id": 74218,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Дай этой функции имя в camel case.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"nightRoutine\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Lights off&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Alarm set&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"nightRoutine();\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"9\" endIndex=\"21\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"nightroutine\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Lights off\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Alarm set\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>nightRoutine</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Braces",
            "id": 74219,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Отметь код, который принадлежит функции.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"morningRoutine\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Lights on&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Alarm off&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"morningRoutine();\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"26\" endIndex=\"27\" /><option startIndex=\"82\" endIndex=\"83\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"function\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Lights on\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Alarm off\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>{</code>, а затем <code>}</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Between braces",
            "id": 74220,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Создай окончательный оператор <code>console.log()</code> внутри функции.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"launch\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;3&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;2&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;1&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Launch!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"launch();\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"78\" endIndex=\"85\" /><option startIndex=\"85\" endIndex=\"86\" /><option startIndex=\"86\" endIndex=\"89\" /><option startIndex=\"90\" endIndex=\"99\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"3\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"2\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"1\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Launch!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>console</code>, затем <code>.</code>, а затем <code>log</code>, <code>\"Launch!\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
